                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am the wife of the prosecutor. I found the purse under the prisoner's bed, which was up in the garret.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17791020-6-person103">
                  HENRY
                   WHITEHOUSE
               <interp inst="t17791020-6-person103" type="surname" value="WHITEHOUSE"></interp>
