                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I was in the house when Mrs. Wilson found the purse, and when she missed the money, and when the boy confessed he had taken it.</p>
               <p>His parents and the master were talking to him? - Yes.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17791020-6-person104">
                  ISAAC
                   MILLER
               <interp inst="t17791020-6-person104" type="surname" value="MILLER"></interp>
