                     <interp inst="t17791020-6-person104" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I was in the house when the prisoner confessed stealing the purse.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I should be glad if you would please to let me go to sea; I would have gone before but my friends were not willing.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17791020-6-verdict42" type="verdictDescription">
